overview: The sinister Scotsman himself, Drew Galloway, sits down with Rob Naylor on the inaugural edition of "Hitting the Highspots."  Drew has been kicking ass all over the world for the going on 15 years, Rob Naylor a former creative assistant for WWE is a walking encyclopedia of wrestling knowledge, put the two together and you've got one of the most entertaining interviews we've ever done!  Highspots proudly brings to you "Hitting the Highspots with Drew Galloway!
title: Hitting The Highspots - Drew Galloway
